---
title: Summertime Pork Schnitzel with Yellow Squash, Tomatoes, and Yukon Golds
description: Comfort food without the guilt? Yes, please. We’ve given this Austrian classic a healthy makeover by ditching the heavy mashed potatoes in favor of a lighter potato and veggie hash. Plus, rather than frying, we bake these pork chops to perfection with an irresistible herbed crust.
